        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "14. we have maintenance from the king's palace—literally, \"we are salted with the salt of the palace.\" \"Eating a prince's salt\" is an Oriental phrase, equivalent to \"receiving maintenance from him.\"",
        "children": []
      }
