    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "\"The letter which you sent to us has been plainly read before me.\" מפרשׁ part. pass. Peal, corresponds with the Hebrew part. Piel מפרשׁ, made plain, adverbially, plainly, and does not signify \"translated into Persian.\"",
